title: PumpRules: Murk in Progress
description: This week on Vanderpump Rules, the Toms plan a party so the rest of the cast can see how they're tumbling into debt. Meanwhile, Brock hatches a plan to have a secret wedding at James and Racquel's engagement party. What could go wrong?
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
